headline: Will Adobe's (ADBE) AI Foundry Launch Reshape Its Edge in Enterprise Content Creation?
summary: Earlier this month, Adobe launched Adobe AI Foundry, an enterprise service enabling businesses to build custom generative AI models using their own branding and intellectual property, with early adoption from companies like Home Depot and Walt Disney Imagineering. This move marks Adobe's deeper entry into enterprise-grade AI, targeting demand for scalable, brand-safe content generation and secure use of proprietary data in creative workflows.
